query:
UPDATE properties SET county = CASE 
  WHEN county = 'City of Laurinburg' THEN 'Scotland'
  WHEN county = 'City of Lumberton' THEN 'Robeson'
  WHEN county = 'Town of Maxton' THEN 'Robeson'
  WHEN county = 'Town of Williamston' THEN 'Martin'
  WHEN county = 'City of Roanoke Rapids' THEN 'Halifax'
  WHEN county = 'Town of Tarboro' THEN 'Edgecombe'
  ELSE county
END
WHERE county IN ('City of Laurinburg', 'City of Lumberton', 'Town of Maxton', 'Town of Williamston', 'City of Roanoke Rapids', 'Town of Tarboro')
